These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, asparagus, pomegranate, lime
1. the person eating raspberry is on the far left##1
2. the person eating asparagus is on the left or right of the person eating raspberry##3
3. the person eating asparagus is on the left or right of the person eating pomegranate##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Food   | raspberry | asparagus | pomegranate | lime |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, mirinda, 7up, hot-chocolate
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | mirinda | lemonade | hot-chocolate | 7up |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, gardening, puzzles, reading
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | sudoku | puzzles | gardening | reading |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, zombie, sports, action
1. the person watching sports movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |  4  |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | fantasy | action | sports |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, rugby, swimming, rowing
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |  3   |     4      |
| Sport   | rowing | swimming | rugby | biathlon |

