.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-10::.
There 4 different types of food: corn, cucumber, pepper, peach
1. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person eating peach##1
2. the person eating cucumber is between the person eating corn and the person eating peach##2
3. the person eating corn is on the left or right of the person eating pepper##3
4. the person eating corn is on the left or right of the person eating pepper##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Food   | peach | cucumber | corn | pepper |

