2. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
3. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2    |     3      |   4    |
| Pet   | cat | rat | goldfish | mouse |

