.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, disco, country, blues
1. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of blues##1
2. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of disco##1
3. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
4. the fan of disco is on the left of the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | country | disco | house | blues |

 